		<title>随着汇价测试关键支撑位，美元兑日元重新被交易者所聚焦</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/market-news/usdjpy-key-support-tested</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 08:40:27 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市场新闻及观点]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[USDJPY]]></category>
